prompt: quiero una landing page de colores verdes
html:
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Green E-commerce Landing Page</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-green: #13ec37; /* Vibrant green for accents */
            --dark-green: #0e8a2b; /* Darker green for buttons/highlights */
            --light-mint: #e0ffe0; /* Very light mint green */
            --white: #ffffff;
            --off-white: #f8f8f8;
            --text-color: #333333;
            --secondary-text-color: #666666;
            --border-color: #e0e0e0;
            --shadow-light: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --roundness: 8px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            color: var(--text-color);
            background-color: var(--off-white);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Header/Navigation */
        header {
            background-color: var(--white);
            padding: 15px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px var(--shadow-light);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-green);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-links {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-color);
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-green);
        }

        .cta-button {
            background-color: var(--dark-green);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: var(--roundness);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #0b6b23; /* Slightly darker green on hover */
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background-color: var(--light-mint);
            text-align: center;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5em;
            color: var(--dark-green);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: var(--secondary-text-color);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .hero-image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: var(--roundness);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px var(--shadow-light);
        }

        /* Products Section */
        .products {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--white);
        }

        .products h2 {
            font-size: 2.8em;
            color: var(--dark-green);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .product-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .product-card {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border-radius: var(--roundness);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px var(--shadow-light);
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            text-align: left;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px var(--shadow-light);
        }

        .product-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .product-info {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .product-info h3 {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        .product-info p {
            font-size: 1em;
            color: var(--secondary-text-color);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .product-price {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-green);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .add-to-cart-button {
            background-color: var(--primary-green);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: var(--roundness);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .add-to-cart-button:hover {
            background-color: var(--dark-green);
        }

        /* Pricing Section */
        .pricing {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background-color: var(--light-mint);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .pricing h2 {
            font-size: 2.8em;
            color: var(--dark-green);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .pricing-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: stretch;
        }

        .price-card {
            background-color: var(--white);
            border-radius: var(--roundness);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px var(--shadow-light);
            padding: 40px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .price-card.highlighted {
            border-color: var(--primary-green);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(19, 236, 55, 0.2);
            transform: scale(1.03);
        }

        .price-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px var(--shadow-light);
        }

        .price-card h3 {
            font-size: 2em;
            color: var(--dark-green);
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .price-card .price {
            font-size: 3em;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-green);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .price-card .price span {
            font-size: 0.5em;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: var(--secondary-text-color);
        }

        .price-card ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .price-card ul li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: var(--text-color);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .price-card ul li::before {
            content: 'âœ“';
            color: var(--primary-green);
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .price-card .select-plan-button {
            background-color: var(--dark-green);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: var(--roundness);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .price-card .select-plan-button:hover {
            background-color: #0b6b23;
        }

        /* Contact Section */
        .contact {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            background-color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact h2 {
            font-size: 2.8em;
            color: var(--dark-green);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .contact-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 40px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .contact-form {
            background-color: var(--off-white);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: var(--roundness);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px var(--shadow-light);
            text-align: left;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .contact-form .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .contact-form label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        .contact-form input[type="text"],
        .contact-form input[type="email"],
        .contact-form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: var(--roundness);
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1em;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: border-color 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-form input[type="text"]:focus,
        .contact-form input[type="email"]:focus,
        .contact-form textarea:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary-green);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(19, 236, 55, 0.2);
            outline: none;
        }

        .contact-form textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 120px;
        }

        .contact-form .submit-button {
            background-color: var(--dark-green);
            color: var(--white);
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: var(--roundness);
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            width: auto;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .contact-form .submit-button:hover {
            background-color: #0b6b23;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .contact-info {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--secondary-text-color);
        }

        .contact-info a {
            color: var(--primary-green);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-info a:hover {
            color: var(--dark-green);
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .social-icons {
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .social-icons a {
            color: var(--dark-green);
            font-size: 1.8em;
            transition: color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .social-icons a:hover {
            color: var(--primary-green);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: var(--dark-green);
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        footer p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .hero {
                flex-direction: row;
                text-align: left;
                padding: 100px 20px;
                gap: 60px;
            }

            .hero-content {
                flex: 1;
            }

            .hero-image {
                flex: 1;
            }

            .product-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }

            .pricing-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            }

            .contact-content {
                flex-direction: row;
                text-align: left;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .contact-form, .contact-info {
                flex: 1;
            }

            .social-icons {
                justify-content: flex-start;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
            }
            .products h2, .pricing h2, .contact h2 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            .nav-links {
                display: none; /* Hide nav links on small screens for simplicity, could add a hamburger menu */
            }
            nav {
                justify-content: center;
            }
            .cta-button {
                display: none; /* Hide cta button on small screens for simplicity */
            }
        }
    </style>
    <!-- Font Awesome for social icons -->
